column1: [{"classname": "angry", "wiki": "Displaying or feeling anger."}, {"classname": "disgusted", "wiki": "Filled with disgust."}, {"classname": "fearful", "wiki": "Frightening."}, {"classname": "happy", "wiki": "Having a feeling arising from a consciousness of well-being or of enjoyment; enjoying good of any kind, such as comfort, peace, or tranquillity; blissful, contented, joyous."}, {"classname": "neutral", "wiki": "Not taking sides in a conflict such as war; nonaligned."}, {"classname": "sad", "wiki": "Emotionally negative."}, {"classname": "surprised", "wiki": "Caused to feel surprise, amazement or wonder, or showing an emotion due to an unexpected event."}]
